Class Summary
admin admin servlet used to create the HTML admin UI (simple or full, "gui" parameter)
admin HTML UI, calls admin servlet to perform actions (reboot, restart Earth, Xorg, purge squid)
closeBalloon closeBalloon servlet used by HTML user interface to close the current info balloon

CreateCsvLuceneIndexRam  
CustomFrenchAnalyzer Deprecated.
DataForEarth Bean holding data for a placemark
flyTo  
flyToPlacemark  
FrenchNormalizer simple French characters translator to non accented ones.
getKmlSync getKmlSync servlet sends a KML response with the right updates for each big Earth instance
also used as a heart beat supervision for every big Earth instance (that is supposed to call getKmlSync once per second), if the grace period expires and rebootcount is positive a restart (earth/Xorg) is demanded.
HeartBeats XY coordinates to hostname translation used for big Earth screen heart beats
LuceneIndex Deprecated.
Mappings Hostname to IP, and IP to hostname mappings used to determine the calling host for reset, pixel servlets.
pixel pixel servlet used by the HTML info balloons to get a transparent pixel in the response, and send the server the ID of the info balloon opened.
used as a heart beat to detect when info balloons are closed on the earth interface, to synch with the screen overlays
response will be a transparent pixel from a request forward to /transparent.gif if will render nice in a HTML info balloon
reset reset servlet used by the html user interface to send a flyTo default location.
response can be ignored
search search servlet used by the html user interface to find information about the custom 3D models (architect, description, ...)
based on the Lucene samples org.apache.lucene.demo.SearchFiles
